{"TopicId":138807,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"That motorcycle from Akira","CreatedByName":"Colonel Cbplayer","CreatedById":102399,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-03T02:14:50Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Colonel Cbplayer","CreatedById":102399,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-03T02:14:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI did my best to make a functioning akira bike to test the wheel physics and it turn out pretty great in the end.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNeeds those little training wheels there so it can actually turn without spinning out, other wised it drives pretty great at high speeds and can even drift.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately the file\u00A0was lost with the pre-release so I need to make it again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/Uq8cj/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe actual Akira bike looks like this for comparison\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.timflattery.com/content/work/07.akira/6.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00226.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"duk","CreatedById":131720,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-03T22:02:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the way it look good job\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Colonel Cbplayer","CreatedById":102399,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-03T22:43:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222559397\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022138807\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221462312959\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022131720\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022duk\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n40 minutes ago, duk said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the way it look good job\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the complement\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI get it rebuild soon\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"chadgaskerman","CreatedById":155837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-04T16:10:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI suggest using the , I want to say ruggedized? wheel as the attachment point/ strut thing gives it bad lines\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbut other than that this is an awesome build\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#00FF00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:48px;\u0022\u003EREEEEEEP!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-04T16:12:04Z\u0022 title=\u002205/04/2016 04:12  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 4, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by chadgaskerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eand how do I...\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"soulreaver1981","CreatedById":38542,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-04T19:29:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncant you use some reaction wheel to keep the bike upright????\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Colonel Cbplayer","CreatedById":102399,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-04T21:28:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222561292\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022138807\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221462390162\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002238542\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022soulreaver1981\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, soulreaver1981 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncant you use some reaction wheel to keep the bike upright????\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt not to keep it upright.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe 2 wheels give it extra traction to the ground and there are plenty of reaction wheels\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe bike itself is extremely stable, however it has a nasty habit of spinning out of control and the wheels help prevent this. The bike handles more like a car really\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-04T21:30:47Z\u0022 title=\u002205/04/2016 09:30  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 4, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by cbplayer2012\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}